# Notes and ref-style fragment frame.

ReferenceFlow[sequence]:
  - Browser[actor]
  - Gateway[service]
  - Auth[service]
  - note over Browser, Gateway: "TLS session established"
  - ref "AuthorizeUser(token)":
      - sync Gateway -> Auth: "validate token"
      - reply Auth -> Gateway: "claims"
  - sync Browser -> Gateway: "GET /account"
  - reply Gateway -> Browser: "account"
